', NULL, '<ul>
	<li>This is a process measure about the timeliness of treatment.</li>
	<li>It is NOT a clinical outcomes measure based on TIMI flow or clinical&nbsp;reperfusion. It does not matter whether the baseline angiogram showed TIMI 3 flow or if the final post-PCI angiogram showed&nbsp;TIMI 0 flow.</li>
