<li>If more than one is available, code the rhythm based on the rhythm strip or ECG closest to&nbsp;the start of the procedure.</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'IMPACT Registry v1.0.1', NULL, 'Pre-Procedure Atrial Ectopic Tachycardia (AET)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 720, '2016-09-14 15:57:00', '2018-08-08 13:13:55', NULL);
