<li>3. the sustained (&gt;30 minutes) requirement for parenteral inotropic or vasopressor agents or mechanical support (e.g., IABP,&nbsp;extracorporeal circulation, ventricular assist devices) to maintain systolic blood pressure &gt;=90 mm Hg, and/or</li>
<li>4. the sustained (&gt;30 minutes) requirement for parenteral inotropic or vasopressor agents or mechanical support (e.g., IABP,&nbsp;extracorporeal circulation, ventricular assist devices) to maintain CI &gt;=2.2 L/min/m2</li>
