<li>Severely reduced = 20%</li>
<li>The Left Ventricular Ejection Fraction can be assessed via invasive (i.e. LV gram) or non-invasive (i.e. Echo, MR, CT or Nuclear) testing.</li>
</ul>', 'CathPCI Registry v4.4', NULL, 'Pre-PCI Left Ventricular Ejection Fraction', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 770, '2016-09-14 15:57:00', '2018-01-05 16:11:49', NULL);
