<li>With atrial flutter, there is a sawtooth pattern of regular atrial activation.</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<ul>
<li>Indicate the patient''s cardiac rhythm. It is acceptable to code the patient''s cardiac rhythm based on cardiac rhythm strips (as&nbsp;opposed to 12 lead ECGs) that are interpreted by a qualified professional.</li>
