', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;<strong>Vessel Patency:</strong></p>

<ul>
	<li>Vessel patency at a given time point will be determined by the absence of&nbsp;&nbsp;clinically-driven target lesion revascularization and/or absence of recurrent target lesion&nbsp;&nbsp;diameter stenosis &gt; 50% by imaging (e.g., invasive angiography or most commonly, duplex&nbsp;&nbsp;ultrasonography).</li>
	<li>If patency data are incorporated within the primary endpoint of a clinical&nbsp;&nbsp;trial, the angiographic images or duplex ultrasonographic images should be assessed by&nbsp;&nbsp;appropriate core laboratories and made available to the CEC for review upon request.</li>
</ul>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
', NULL, 'CDISC August 20, 2014', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 775, '2016-09-14 15:57:00', '2016-09-14 15:56:26', NULL);
