', NULL, '<p><strong>Step 1.</strong></p>

<ul>
	<li>Bring the measuring tape around your back to the front, keeping it under the arms and bringing it up across to the middle of your chest (see image). If you get an odd number, round up to the next even number to get your band size.</li>
